# SplitWave — Expense Splitter App Framework

## Tech Stack

- **Frontend:** React (Vite)
- **Backend:** Node.js + Express
- **Database:** PostgreSQL (via Prisma ORM)
- **Auth:** Firebase Auth (Google + Phone OTP)
- **Currency API:** ExchangeRate-API (live rates, updated hourly)
- **AI Receipt Scanner:** OpenAI GPT-4o Vision API
- **Notifications:** Firebase Cloud Messaging (FCM)
- **File Storage:** Firebase Storage (receipt images)
- **Hosting:** Vercel (frontend) + Railway (backend)

