## Recommended Build Order

```
Phase 1 — Foundation
  1. Prisma schema + DB setup
  2. Firebase Auth + auth middleware
  3. User profile (register / login)

Phase 2 — Core Features
  4. Group CRUD (create, add members, view)
  5. Expense CRUD (add expense, equal split only)
  6. Balance calculator + debt simplification
  7. Mark settled

Phase 3 — Currency
  8. ExchangeRate-API integration
  9. Currency converter page
  10. Multi-currency group split (store in INR, display in home currency)

Phase 4 — Smart Split
  11. Percentage split (sliders)
  12. Exact split (manual amounts)
  13. Itemized split (manual items)

Phase 5 — Unique Features
  14. AI receipt scanner (GPT-4o Vision)
  15. Spending personality + analytics charts
  16. Nudge system (FCM push)
  17. Recurring expenses (cron job)
  18. Spin-to-pay wheel
  19. Timeline view

Phase 6 — Polish
  20. Mobile responsiveness
  21. Empty states + error handling
  22. Loading skeletons
  23. Deploy (Vercel + Railway)
```